content: AIFlowML: Made substantial code changes this month with 14 merged PRs, primarily focused on bug fixes for various plugins and Biome configurations (+59,888/-373,996 lines total). Notable contributions include major refactoring work on local AI plugins through PRs #3704, #3663, and #3526, collectively adding over 44,000 lines while removing approximately 30,000 lines. Most activity was concentrated on configuration files (48%) and code (37%), with an occasional contribution pattern spread across 8 days of the month.
